s_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564088903","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546328980,"updated_time":1546328980,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主已经证明了，如果高中生自称能证明哥德巴赫猜想，就有机会在一星期内获得上万的粉丝o(╯□╰)o\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e此处 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/3782418f0f3f84cca3ba3249f2c61ffc\" data-hash=\"3782418f0f3f84cca3ba3249f2c61ffc\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$3782418f0f3f84cca3ba3249f2c61ffc\"\u003e@凡伟\u003c/a\u003e 自古英雄出少年，还是得学习一个~\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560938524,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a4f57186d81e066dd8b81087433a41c8","url_token":"zhu-liu-liu-36","name":"猪六六","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-200c417ba8390c6cb1beaba1c32ae10f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-200c417ba8390c6cb1beaba1c32ae10f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a4f57186d81e066dd8b81087433a41c8","user_type":"people","headline":"正义永不会缺席","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560938524","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-5f73d08f4dd158066978e2462ab706dd_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545900528,"updated_time":1545971638,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我突然奇想，有了灵感\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题目：如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e解答过程，采用举例法\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1、若该高中生证明了哥德巴赫猜想，一定会被保送清华北大\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e思路1、因：中南大学刘路破解西塔潘猜想，刘路被保送硕博连读\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e又因：西塔潘猜想难度\u0026lt;\u0026lt;哥德巴赫猜想  \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e      保送硕博连读≈保送清华北大数学系\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可得：破解哥德巴赫猜想可以保送清华北大\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e思路2、因2018年清华北大保送资格共计372人，附名单\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d3ada06fcadf547467f5339010ee80ca_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"525\" data-rawheight=\"3524\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-132e48c0f85af87ffdb6c926717044c2_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"525\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d3ada06fcadf547467f5339010ee80ca_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='525'%20height='3524'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"525\" data-rawheight=\"3524\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-132e48c0f85af87ffdb6c926717044c2_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"525\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d3ada06fcadf547467f5339010ee80ca_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d3ada06fcadf547467f5339010ee80ca_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e又因：奥赛国家队集训学生\u0026lt;\u0026lt;奥赛国家队队长and奥赛国家队教练\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e      奥赛国家队队长and奥赛国家队教练无法证明哥德巴赫猜想\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 可得：证明哥德巴赫猜想\u0026gt;\u0026gt;奥赛国家队队长and国家队教练\u0026gt;\u0026gt;奥赛国家队集训学生\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可证：证明哥德巴赫猜想，必被保送清华北大\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e思路3、2014年菲尔兹奖获得者玛利亚姆·米尔扎哈尼 美国（伊朗籍），获奖原因“对黎曼曲面及其模空间的动力学和几何作出了突出的贡献”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e因：黎曼猜想=哥德巴赫猜想=四色定理\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e    证明、破解\u0026gt;\u0026gt;做出突出贡献\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可得：证明哥德巴赫猜想必获得菲尔兹奖\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e又因：刘晓彤（女排奥运冠军）被清华招录为硕士研究生\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e     菲尔兹奖\u0026gt;\u0026gt;奥运冠军\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e     硕士研究生\u0026gt;本科生\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可得：获得菲尔兹奖必被清华大学录取\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e上述证明中，充分必要条件为“破解哥德巴赫猜想”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e若充分必要条件不成立，证明不成立\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560427288,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3f9f4bd89176a65a757d0905d657891e","url_token":"alice-26-89","name":"still alice","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f0c02fbe095d0623c9021aa9c4330f48_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f0c02fbe095d0623c9021aa9c4330f48_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3f9f4bd89176a65a757d0905d657891e","user_type":"people","headline":"庸人自扰","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560427288","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545836900,"updated_time":1545836900,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e可不可以其他评论已经有回答了，我也是外行人，数学不太好，是个美术生。曾经满腔热血想考美院，最终去了一个微不足道的小学校。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我理解你这样想追着希望的感觉。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e非常非常希望你真的可以证出来，可以实现自己的梦想。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560800289,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3dd4ea7514d05b228ee4a0c046a13383","url_token":"du-de-chi-wan","name":"小庚","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/dd68fd5232ad889e98471222b435f816_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/dd68fd5232ad889e98471222b435f816_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3dd4ea7514d05b228ee4a0c046a13383","user_type":"people","headline":"汽车cae工程师/madymo/汽车碰撞安全","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560800289","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545889028,"updated_time":1545889028,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e居然有这么多人还等着要看他的证明。我想我真的是高看知乎了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大家是真不知道哥德巴赫猜想有多难？还是大家都在等着看猴子？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560871007,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"917f72547120979d3d7899bf845fd360","url_token":"zhou-dan-26-6","name":"肝能补脸","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/9c5cf048847b07d6596a9b22da89e69e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/9c5cf048847b07d6596a9b22da89e69e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/917f72547120979d3d7899bf845fd360","user_type":"people","headline":"克莱登大学马房山校区第九（女）宿舍管理员","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560871007","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545895120,"updated_time":1545987640,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不会，你会直接拿到藤校终身教职的offer。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e或者这么说，全世界的一流高校都会抢着给你教授的职位。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e睡醒了没有？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e醒了，就去复习吧，先定个小目标。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e把高考数学考个满分玩儿玩儿，你说呢？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562833030,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"097c9c03b85cfced0efcd50bbe437e57","url_token":"yi-ru-40-72","name":"易如","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/097c9c03b85cfced0efcd50bbe437e57","user_type":"people","headline":"无业游民","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562833030","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546151511,"updated_time":1546151511,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这里我理解“会被清华北大数学系保送吗”，指的是去清北的数学系读本科。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高中生证明出了哥德巴赫猜想猜想，99.9999999999%的可能性是和大多数民科一样，只是自己觉得证出来了，没可能被数学界承认是正确的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e好了，这不还有0.0000000001%的可能性吗？如果真的是这样，起码他应该看过陈景润证明的1+2，看过潘承洞的《哥德巴赫猜想猜想》，看过怀尔斯证明菲尔马大定理的证明，等等等等。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说明这娃娃已经数学功底深厚了，那还去什么清北读书学习的本科，难道不是直接去当教授博导吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以题主的问题的答案是“否定”。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559439529,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"64b70caddf6e9c656bd2a0ae11f676a0","url_token":"yanb-14","name":"就叫我小豹子吧","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/23fd1f79d918959015f9be28cf284aa5_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/23fd1f79d918959015f9be28cf284aa5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/64b70caddf6e9c656bd2a0ae11f676a0","user_type":"people","headline":"嗷呜嗷呜","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559439529","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545727020,"updated_time":1545727020,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e北大清华对你来说屈才了，教育部部长应该你来当，你把你的思维方式和论证方法编入教材，为国家培养更多像你这样的人才俊杰，在中华民族的历史上留下你伟大的名字才应该是符合你才能的方式。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560031667,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4c6644dcdcec98d6e49a9198232672b3","url_token":"tang-leefk","name":"唐LEEFK","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2cb727da7aab9d53c71b9e90c94a303d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2cb727da7aab9d53c71b9e90c94a303d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4c6644dcdcec98d6e49a9198232672b3","user_type":"people","headline":"内燃机，战列舰，GPU","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560031667","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545803336,"updated_time":1545803336,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不如同时发一份到arxiv？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560978032,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b4c1340a3275c87604bd54e40b2f76ae","url_token":"mu-wei-33-5","name":"牧威","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4536a78f54c6a309ad600d07b6ec4a2d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4536a78f54c6a309ad600d07b6ec4a2d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b4c1340a3275c87604bd54e40b2f76ae","user_type":"people","headline":"笨鸟久飞，也可入林。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560978032","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545903903,"updated_time":1545903903,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不是专搞数学的，不过就我浅薄的数学水平对哥猜的了解来说，提出这个问题，应该是还没证明出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e简单地说，目前哥猜的意义不在于哥猜本身，而在于证明的过程。之所以一直没有被证明，一般认为两种可能原因：一，没有足够好的工具，包括数学工具，也包括计算机；二，目前的工具已经够了，只是还没有人能提出足够严谨的证明思路。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e话说回来，如果这位高中生真的证明了，那么不论是走第一条路——自己研发出了一个工具来证明，还是第二条路——设计出了足够严谨的证明思路。他所需要的，就不是清北本科的资源了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这样的人才，从教育的角度来看，完全可以自己翻看教材学到极致；从结识数学大牛的角度来看，他不需要主动；从学历的角度来看，他的能力足够碾压“学历规则”。清北本科还有什么可以吸引他的么？帅哥美女？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e目前还没开箱，谁也不知道结果。如果真的证明出来了，建议这位同学提高一点眼界，不要只想着保送清北本科，起码往殿堂看看；如果假的，也不要灰心，因为哥猜就像希尔伯特说费尔马大定理“一只会下金蛋的母鸡”，你不一定要想着吃这只母鸡的肉，能让它下出蛋来，也是莫大的本事。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562095638,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c0ffbc8208cdcd9e95b88796b50e17ec","url_token":"938574874lfx","name":"翔中之王","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-31a0057cce9d088960cc37146eab79