280651848b82984f8905","user_type":"people","headline":"傻子赢了","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562999768","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546171075,"updated_time":1546228270,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e    他会直接成为TG总书记。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e    其实都一样，反正他都做不到。    \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e    退三亿六千八百万步来说，假如题主真的证明了，他必然是国家的栋梁，民族的希望，从此中国在国际的数学地位必然拔高。若果真如此，我便是被打脸，也是国之幸甚！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e    我欢迎他来打我脸，我不会感到羞耻，我会替他骄傲。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e    这件事儿的真实性还比不上八百年前的割肾谣言。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1，这瓜娃子没搞懂哥德巴赫猜想是个什么级别的玩意儿，能问出这种问题的人，至少不可能指望他来吧……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2，都高三的人了，学校里没举办过数学竞赛嘛？你都能证明哥德巴赫猜想了，就那些题目难得倒你？一路全面绿灯好吧……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3，我个人绝对不相信一个有能力证明哥德巴赫猜想的人，在搞掂了这个难题后第一反应是到知乎骗粉骗关注。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就酱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果他真的证明了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他是中国的脊梁，前途无量\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果他只是个哗众取宠的小丑\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我相信广大pang友一定会让他体会一下什么叫网络暴力\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563746476,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7eee9265a481043ffcc8676db6d47f7d","url_token":"chen-chen-86-56-93","name":"阳哥","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-296874f536d02dbbae6ace8b3a11a151_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-296874f536d02dbbae6ace8b3a11a151_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7eee9265a481043ffcc8676db6d47f7d","user_type":"people","headline":"专业给薛定谔解方程","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563746476","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d7a858c64f9a8e24c51057a1a755725f_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546271667,"updated_time":1546271667,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我不是来答题，我是来围观的，因为在写道题中插播的广告是这样：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-42c91301a788b019c0ded58ecfe82305_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"1334\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f977165252da2b1bf63edfe212a98a6e_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"750\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-42c91301a788b019c0ded58ecfe82305_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='750'%20height='1334'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"1334\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f977165252da2b1bf63edfe212a98a6e_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"750\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-42c91301a788b019c0ded58ecfe82305_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-42c91301a788b019c0ded58ecfe82305_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e望诸位保护好自己的身体\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560484602,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7c71ec98fac98e69ca8f799a9e381785","url_token":"ji-shi-75-72","name":"撒了欢的人工智能","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6bc2c64b841eee6c80279555f321aa64_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6bc2c64b841eee6c80279555f321aa64_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7c71ec98fac98e69ca8f799a9e381785","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560484602","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545841712,"updated_time":1545841775,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我个人十分想看是怎么证明的。把证明过程放到专门的网站上，再转载到知乎。感觉知乎也有点乱，毕竟只有在专业的领域的大神才会告诉你是对是错，哪里错了，你可以跟他们去辩论。年少不是错，错在请教的不是地方。然后我个人觉得只有和水平相当的人（或者更高也行）讨论才会让自己的思路更清晰，思维更严谨。知乎这里只是一个信息收集平台（当然也是个人见解）。把证明贴出来，就算是错的，也比在评论下面耍嘴皮子的人强。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e个人还是想看你的证明过程。这个是唯一的关注点。真的好好奇你是怎么证明的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560574091,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7db38efcad2980f576e6c9b87c4d533a","url_token":"mo-ji-ty","name":"墨迹ty","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/becced4d3e7ddfc1a846c3b4e580f66f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/becced4d3e7ddfc1a846c3b4e580f66f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7db38efcad2980f576e6c9b87c4d533a","user_type":"people","headline":"可怜你帅不过坂本大佬","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560574091","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545870258,"updated_time":1545870258,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我觉得一个高中生有勇气去证明哥德巴赫猜想这件事本身就很了不起了，如果高考不能让一个人充分发挥自己的才能，答主想为自己找一条喜欢的出路又有什么可以指责？我不懂数学，但是我可以理解答主想为自己搏一搏的心情\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在知乎发表论文的确没有用，你可以考虑直接联系校方或者教授。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然现在未必证明得了，但是将来的事谁说的准呢？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=580\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=540\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2283}}
